《'''环太平洋：电影原声带'''》（{{lang-en|Pacific Rim: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack}}）是2013年上映的美国[[科幻电影|科幻电影]]《'''[[环太平洋_(电影)|环太平洋]]'''》的电影原声音乐专辑。本张原声专辑由德籍伊朗裔作曲家[[拉敏·贾瓦迪|拉敏·贾瓦迪]]负责编曲制作，美韩混血唱作人[[Priscilla_Ahn|普丽希拉·安]]<ref name="FMR" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/BatFreak/news/?a=81533 |title=Release Date And Track List For The PACIFIC RIM Soundtrack Unveiled |publisher=ComicBookMovie.com |date=2013-06-13 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029183915/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/BatFreak/news/?a=81533 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和美国吉他演奏家[[汤姆·莫雷洛|汤姆·莫雷洛]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=191856 |title=RAGE AGAINST THE MACHINE Guitarist On 'Pacific Rim' Soundtrack - June 28, 2013 |publisher=[[Blabbermouth.net|Blabbermouth.net]] |date=2013-06-28 |accessdate=2013-10-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/tom-morello-marches-with-ramin-djawadi-on-pacific-rim-song-premiere-20130624 |title=Tom Morello Marches with Ramin Djawadi on ''Pacific Rim'' Song Premiere |author=Cubarrubia, RJ |publisher=''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]'' |date=2013-06-24 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210233351/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/tom-morello-marches-with-ramin-djawadi-on-pacific-rim-song-premiere-20130624 |dead-url=no }}</ref>也参与了本次的制作；此外，参与这张原声制作的交响乐团的人数超过了100人，包括了一个俄罗斯的合唱团。<ref name="Wired">{{cite web |url=http://www.wired.com/underwire/?p=152231 |title=How the ''Game of Thrones'' Composer Scored the Massively Epic Music of ''Pac Rim'' |author=Maloney, Devon |publisher=''[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]'' |date=2013-07-15 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217233932/http://www.wired.com/underwire/?p=152231 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本片导演[[吉尔摩·德尔·托罗|吉尔摩·德尔·托罗]]将本片的配乐工作交给拉敏·贾瓦迪是因为看中了他以往在《[[越狱|越狱]]》、《[[鋼鐵人_(電影)|钢铁侠]]》以及《[[权力的游戏_(电视剧)|权力的游戏]]》等影视作品配乐中的优秀表现。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/guillermo-del-toro-pacific-rim-soundtrack-collectables/|title=Guillermo del Toro Talks ''PACIFIC RIM'' Soundtrack and Collectables|last=Weintraub|first=Steve 'Frosty'|work=collider.com|date=August 8, 2012|accessdate=October 27, 2013|archive-date=2014-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217214530/http://collider.com/guillermo-del-toro-pacific-rim-soundtrack-collectables/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

《环太平洋：电影原声带》分为数字版和实体版两种发售形式。两者在[[亞馬遜公司|亚马逊网络商城]]分别于2013年6月18日与25日上架发售。<ref>{{cite web|title=''Pacific Rim'' on Amazon|url=http://www.amazon.com/Pacific-Soundtrack-Warner-Pictures-Legendary/dp/B00DIJ49UW/ref=sr_1_13?ie=UTF8&qid=1372197168&sr=8-13&keywords=pacific+rim|accessdate=2013-10-26|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107060424/http://www.amazon.com/Pacific-Soundtrack-Warner-Pictures-Legendary/dp/B00DIJ49UW/ref=sr_1_13?ie=UTF8&qid=1372197168&sr=8-13&keywords=pacific+rim|dead-url=no}}</ref> 实体版原声碟于7月9日开始在零售店发售，早于电影正式上映三天的时间。<ref name="FMR" />

